<h2>Slot no longer available</h2>

<p>Hi <%= @request.guest_name %>,</p>

<p>The slot you requested with <strong><%= @nutritionist.name %></strong> is no
longer available — another appointment was accepted for an overlapping time,
so your request was automatically canceled.</p>

<table cellpadding="6" style="border-collapse:collapse;font-family:system-ui,sans-serif;">
  <tr><td><strong>Service</strong></td><td><%= @service.name %></td></tr>
  <tr><td><strong>Requested time</strong></td><td><%= @starts_at.strftime("%A, %B %d, %Y at %H:%M") %></td></tr>
</table>

<p>This wasn't a rejection from <%= @nutritionist.name %> — feel free to book
another time.</p>

<p>— Nutri App</p>
